OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUK heatwave: Parents warned
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto keep children out of sun
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Parents are advised to limit their     
OL,6, children's sun exposure as temperatures
OL,7, are predicted to hit highs of 30C (86F)
OL,8, across parts of the UK.                
OL,10,FChildren should cover up in light      
OL,11,Fcoloured clothing and rest in the      
OL,12,Fshade, a specialist children's hospital
OL,13,Fsays, as a heat-health alert is issued.
OL,15,FTemperatures are expected to rise over 
OL,16,Fthe weekend and remain high for much of
OL,17,Fnext week.                             
OL,19,FHeatwaves are becoming more likely and 
OL,20,Fmore extreme because of climate change.
